<br>
On the last pull, two druids in zone.  No shammies.  No clerics.<br>
<br>
Yes, that's right, 2 druids were all we had for healers.<br>
<br>
And one of them was me, and I was kiting the amy's around.  So we were effectively killing temple with one druid doing the heals.<br>
<br>
This after a night where the chanter was the puller.  Tee hee.  Pulling Fear at 59 is a LOT easier than at earlier levels.  Biggest pull: about 6.  most pulls were singles.  And the big pulls were just 'cause I couldn't find mobs and then got sorta surrounded.<br>
<br>
(For those who haven't figured it out, I was dual-comping.)<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/udlisabella.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DLIsabella</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www25.brinkster.com/sherrih/rabbit.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Scowling Poster</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#778899>(11/15/01 6:27:36 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Who Needs Clerics</span><hr size=1> That druid got a good res? lol<br>
 <p>DLIsabella, 29 Mage of Innoruuk
<br>
Sherilyn, 52 Cleric of Innoruuk<br>
Lilsherilyn, 55 Mage of Innoruuk<br><br>
